imdb.plot outline: Star Trek Secret Voyage is a Fan-Made web-series production chronicling "The Final Classic Adventure of the 23rd Century", taking place after the completion of the U.S.S. Enterprise's 5 year mission under legendary Captain James T. Kirk and before the events portrayed in "Star Trek: The Motion Picture". Join a new crew assembled by Starfleet for a covert mission, that bridges the gaps within Star Trek History celebrating 45 years of STAR TREK.
